            <title>[SOLR-8194] Improve error reporting UpdateRequest</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8194</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SolrJ throws NPE if null documents are added to UpdateRequest. It should report a proper error message so i don&apos;t get confused the next time i skrew up. Please see: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mail-archive.com/solr-user@lucene.apache.org/msg115074.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.mail-archive.com/solr-user@lucene.apache.org/msg115074.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
